- Dropping DPVS entirely (post-x64 evaluation). gl11/D3D11 as x64 (Phase 34). Miles 9.3b audio x64 
port (Phase 35). redist-d3dx9 fallback for the asm path (contingency checkpoint only). Door-snap 
(VERIFY-01) / OOM-class (VERIFY-02) confirmation (Phase 36).
</user_constraints>

