Current asm call site (master, VERIFIED grep 2026-06-17):
  Direct3d9_VertexShaderData.cpp:749-757 â€” builds the D3DXMACRO define array (the vTextureCoord
    defines built earlier + D3DXMACRO d = {"TARGET", target} at :750 + the {NULL,NULL} terminator at 
:755).
  :759 IncludeHandler includeHandler (the TreeFile-routed handler, shared with the HLSL path).
  :760 D3DXAssembleShader(m_compileText, m_compileTextLength, &(ms_defines.front()), 
&includeHandler, 0,
       &compiledShader, NULL).
