Fix-A.
  :766 CreateVertexShader(reinterpret_cast<DWORD const*>(compiledShader->GetBufferPointer()), ...).

NOTE: D3DXMACRO is ABI-identical to D3D_SHADER_MACRO; ID3DXBuffer is ABI-identical to ID3DBlob; the
IncludeHandler implements the ID3DXInclude vtable which is ABI-identical to ID3DInclude â€” so a
reinterpret_cast at the call boundary is the same technique the 32-02 HLSL path already uses (see 
:178-183).
The HLSL path (D3DCompile) already migrated; this plan migrates the ONE remaining D3DXAssembleShader 
