2. Resolve `PFN_D3DAssemble` ONCE via a static-local: `static const HMODULE s_d3dc = 
LoadLibraryA("d3dcompiler_47.dll"); static const PFN_D3DAssemble s_d3dAssemble = s_d3dc ? 
