<threat_model>
## Trust Boundaries

| Boundary | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| GPU surface/texture data -> own-impl LockRect/memcpy blit | Surface bytes copied via a manual 
lock-blit instead of D3DX; same trusted GPU-resident render data, no new external input |

