| Threat ID | Category | Component | Disposition | Mitigation Plan |
|-----------|----------|-----------|-------------|-----------------|
| T-33-06 | Tampering (correctness) | own-impl LockRect/memcpy surface blit (pitch handling) | 
mitigate | Honor the LockRect pitch row-by-row (a wrong pitch corrupts the copy); Task 4 A/B render 
confirms the copied surfaces (RT, texture) render correct |
| T-33-07 | (input/network/auth/crypto) | â€” | accept/N-A | No new input, network, auth, session, 
or crypto surface â€” matrix math + surface copy + file save are internal render-state operations on 
trusted local data (33-RESEARCH.md Security Domain: V5/V6/V2/V3/V4 all N/A) |

All other ASVS categories N/A â€” Phase 33 adds no input/network/auth/session/crypto surface.
</threat_model>

