A live-tree spot check confirms the D3DX residuals are real and concentrated in the D3D9 plugin, and 
the DPVS guard issue is real: `DPVS_CPU_X86` is currently unconditional for Win32. It also confirms 
the Miles surface is broad enough that Plan 05 should avoid per-call edits unless it can prove zero 
x64 `AIL_*` symbols at object/link level.
