.planning\ROADMAP.md:141:#### Phase 32: D3DX to d3dcompiler_47
.planning\ROADMAP.md:142:**Goal**: The legacy D3DX shader-compile path is ported to `d3dcompiler_47` 
(`D3DCompile`) and D3DX is removed from the build, eliminating the x64-hostile dependency that 
blocks a clean x64 link - landing the v2.3-deferred HARD-05 as a true prerequisite for the first x64 
client.
