caches **raw** bytes; a 2nd `#include` of the same `.inc` in one compile can return **unrewritten** 
text unless the plan specifies rewrite-on-cache-insert. gl11 rewrites on every `Open`; D3D9 does 
not. | `Direct3d9_VertexShaderData.cpp:153-170`; `32-02-PLAN.md:209-211` |
