`_USRDLL;DIRECT3D9_EXPORTS` for the plugin and `NDEBUG;DEBUG_LEVEL=0` for Release, while 
`SwgClient.vcxproj` uses `_WINDOWS` and per-config iterator/debug defines. A single platform-only 
props file cannot safely replace per-config/per-target definitions.
